    "Most of the code bases are written in various programming languages, each with its own syntax and semantics.",
    "Developing deep learning models that generalize well across different languages is a considerable challenge.",
    "Currently, most of the studies in deep learningbased refactoring use applications written in Java.",
    "Thus, there is little or no slow adoption in other programming languages.",
    "Another challenge concerning the generalization is to make the approaches applicable to all categories of code smells."
